
Collection of unrelated utility scripts (well, there's only one for now).

# Descriptions

### Turbo exec toggle

Script to use in conjunction with the [turbo exec package](/common/turbo_exec), this allows you to toggle turbo exec with a hotkey.
Useful for simple use-cases of turbo exec where you just want to make one of your scripts run faster.

You can edit the number of cycles per frame you want by editing the first line of the script. The default is 500.

Default hotkey : **E**

# Import codes

Name|Requirements|Import Code
:-:|---|:--
